        ]
      },
      "date": "2018-09-20 17:01:19.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nPassed enforced test review-ldiskfs on CentOS 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-34vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/fdd5bff2-03c0-48f5-ab38-1dec2ad9cfb0 ran 4 tests.",
