      "date": "2018-09-20 17:58:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nDoes it mean that we will check and skip every OSC in the list every time?  What if there are 300 OSCs?  Then the first 100 will be processed, then the second 100 will be processed on the next call, but will the first 100 timeout before we get to the 300th or 1000th or 2000th OSC?",
